    "Warrant": "The Constitution guarantees the right to vote to all citizens with voting rights, and no law can deprive or restrict this right based on residency abroad.",
    "Backing": "The commenter implicitly uses the Constitution as a basis for the right to vote.",
    "Qualifier": "None",
    "Rebuttal": "None"
  },
